@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = course-alex-local-token

### Retrieval-only knowledge position
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "How do I recover a locked account?",
  "conversationId": "prod-02-knowledge",
  "position": "knowledge"
}

### Governed ticket resolver position
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Create a ticket about missing recovery emails",
  "conversationId": "prod-02-ticket",
  "position": "ticket"
}

### Explicit approved mode wins over position mapping
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Create a ticket about missing recovery emails",
  "conversationId": "prod-02-explicit",
  "position": "ticket",
  "mode": "support_assistant"
}

### Unknown mode remains a visible strict-routing failure
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Create a ticket",
  "conversationId": "prod-02-unknown-mode",
  "position": "ticket",
  "mode": "untrusted_admin"
}

### Unknown position is rejected by the application resolver
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/assistant/orchestrate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Create a ticket",
  "conversationId": "prod-02-unknown-position",
  "position": "admin-console"
}
